pe and today’s iterations of traditional Chinese Medicine as well.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aMedicine, ChinesevEarly works to 1800. 0aMedicine, Chinese. 7aMEDICAL / Acupuncture.2bisacsh  aacademic.  aancient china.  achinese medicine.  achinese translation.  aeastern medicine.  aeastern philosophy.  aeastern world.  ahealing tradition.  ahealing.  ahippocraticum.  amedical doctor.  amedical practitioner.  amedical treatment.  amedical.  amedicinal.  amedicine.  anatural laws.  anatural world.  anature.  ascholarly.  asecular.  atraditional.  atranslation.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Complete eBook-Package 2016z97831106675470 cprintz978052029225340uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052096582940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520965829423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520965829/original  a978-3-11-066754-7  University of California Press Complete eBook-Package 2016b2016  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY